{"tid":147410,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麥記搵靚女送餐","createTime":"2017-03-07T22:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T09:48:11.000Z","uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efed88e6ce24c0a404838d8c218144fc48fc996e","tid":147410,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T22:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170308/large/08lp2p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170308%2Flarge%2F08lp2p05.jpg&h=69d7848a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n充當model嘅女店員來自又一城分店，笑容滿分。<br />\n<br />\n男人一生，只為尋覓一個肯同自己捱麥記嘅女人，不過，如果兩口子食食吓漢堡包，男士又見到個靚女店員，又會唔會開始有選擇困難症呢？<br />\n<br />\n麥記前晚邀請傳媒晚宴介紹新計劃，席間由幾個小妹妹，捧住麥記新推嘅包出嚟，傳媒以為係model，但麥當勞董事總經理黎韋詩話呀：「好靚女呢，但唔係model嚟，係我哋新增嘅服務團隊成員。」佢話成員會喺60間全新Experience of the Future（EotF）店服務，包括新增嘅送餐及顧客服務等。<br />\n<br />\n呢班女店員喺現場獲邀充當model影相，有男性傳媒人好關心咁問其中一位少女：「你喺邊間分店做呀？」。佢大方答：「又一城呀。」唔知呢間分店，之後會唔會多咗男士光顧？"},{"pid":"a8c51a4612aa3bd1521fee3faf702c117bb724fb","tid":147410,"uid":913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:00:54.000Z","msg":"說好的靚女?"},{"pid":"0b65419b771d0618dce916cde99e37f1d4d44cb1","tid":147410,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:01:59.000Z","msg":"麥樂雞幾錢Q?"},{"pid":"577e1f7e785538a9e9cb5d6887c6a9e2b360ad95","tid":147410,"uid":28461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:51:50.000Z","msg":"模特兒黎架緊"},{"pid":"b7421aa5bedf16ef01891808c84b4c03a5f2719a","tid":147410,"uid":28461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:52:21.000Z","msg":"模特兒黎架<span style=\"color: red;\">炸</span>"},{"pid":"d70a7982e7fba92e13b2c10866ab8bb6e02a8ba5","tid":147410,"uid":29585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:59:23.000Z","msg":"東九龍其中一個path個公關姐姐啲大佬嚟㗎<br />\n不過真喺幾靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 